import React from 'react';
import { Box, Container, Grid, Typography, Button } from '@mui/material';
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom';

const Navbar = () => {
  return (
    <Box sx={{ backgroundColor: '#232323', color: '#fff', py: 2, boxShadow: 2 }}>
      <Container maxWidth="lg">
        <Grid container spacing={4} alignItems="center">
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
            <Typography variant="h5" component="h2" fontFamily="'Roboto', sans-serif" fontWeight="500">
              Tribunal de Commerce à Casablanca
            </Typography>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
            <Grid container justifyContent="center" spacing={3}>
              <Grid item>
                <Link to="/" style={{ textDecoration: 'none', color: '#fff', fontSize: '1rem' }}>
                  Accueil
                </Link>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item>
                <Link to="/login" style={{ textDecoration: 'none', color: '#fff', fontSize: '1rem' }}>
                  Connexion
                </Link>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item>
                <Link to="/register" style={{ textDecoration: 'none', color: '#fff', fontSize: '1rem' }}>
                  Inscription
                </Link>
              </Grid>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
            <Grid container justifyContent="flex-end" spacing={2}>
              <Grid item>
                <Button variant="contained" color="success" sx={{ fontSize: '0.875rem' }}>
                  Contactez-nous
                </Button>
              </Grid>
              <Grid item>
                <Button variant="contained" color="error" sx={{ fontSize: '0.875rem' }}>
                  À propos de nous
                </Button>
              </Grid>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Container>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Navbar;
